Package com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.fluentcore.arm.collection

Interface SupportsGettingByResourceGroup<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the resource to get.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ApplicationGateways, AppServiceCertificateOrders, AppServiceCertificates, AppServiceDomains, AppServicePlans, AvailabilitySets, BatchAccounts, BatchAIClusters, BatchAIFileServers, CdnProfiles, ContainerGroups, ContainerServices, CosmosDBAccounts, Deployments, Disks, DnsZones, EventHubNamespaces, ExpressRouteCircuits, FunctionApps, Identities, KubernetesClusters, LoadBalancers, LocalNetworkGateways, ManagementLocks, NetworkInterfaces, Networks, NetworkSecurityGroups, NetworkWatchers, PublicIPAddresses, RedisCaches, Registries, RouteTables, SearchServices, ServiceBusNamespaces, Snapshots, SqlServers, StorageAccounts, TrafficManagerProfiles, Vaults, VirtualMachineCustomImages, VirtualMachines, VirtualMachineScaleSets, VirtualNetworkGateways, WebApps

    public interface SupportsGettingByResourceGroup<T>
    Provides access to getting a specific Azure resource based on its name and resource group.

    (Note this interface is not intended to be implemented by user code.)
